{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853551010,"sessionID":"ses_286e2102fffeK1Ugk0qqEpAss1","part":{"id":"prt_d791eb15e001WOjYOC9RZAvFC3","messageID":"msg_d791e3d12001UeXOMS1g6shzoi","sessionID":"ses_286e2102fffeK1Ugk0qqEpAss1","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:10","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/notes.md","content":"# AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 - Notes\n\n## Design Notes\n\nTBD - Design notes will be captured during implementation.\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\nTBD - Implementation notes will be captured during development.\n\n## Review Notes\n\nTBD - Review feedback will be captured here.\n\n---\n\n*Status: Draft*\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/notes.md","time":{"start":1775853550989,"end":1775853551010}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853551380,"sessionID":"ses_286e2102fffeK1Ugk0qqEpAss1","part":{"id":"prt_d791e45150015gHPfygSHptwcq","messageID":"msg_d791e3d12001UeXOMS1g6shzoi","sessionID":"ses_286e2102fffeK1Ugk0qqEpAss1","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-008\ntitle: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\nmodule: pkg/workloadmanager\nlanguage: Go\nsize: S\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n# Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n# Language: Go\n# Size: S\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: garbage-collection\n  description: |\n    Implement a scheduled garbage collection mechanism for sandbox resources.\n    This component periodically scans and cleans up expired, idle, or orphaned\n    sandbox instances to reclaim resources and maintain system health. It provides\n    configurable retention policies, cleanup strategies, and observability hooks.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - Scheduled GC task with configurable interval\n    - Expired sandbox detection based on TTL\n    - Idle sandbox detection based on inactivity timeout\n    - Orphaned sandbox cleanup (owner not found)\n    - Resource reclamation metrics\n    - Graceful cleanup with proper finalization\n    - Configurable retention policies per sandbox type\n    - Safe-mode dry-run capability\n    - Event logging for audit trail\n  out:\n    - Sandbox lifecycle management (handled in AR-005/AR-006)\n    - CRD reconciler logic (handled in AR-007)\n    - Multi-cluster GC coordination (separate AR)\n    - External storage cleanup (separate AR)\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - GC runs at configurable intervals (default: 5 minutes)\n  - Expired sandboxes are identified and cleaned up\n  - Idle sandboxes are detected and reclaimed\n  - Orphaned resources are properly handled\n  - Metrics exposed for GC operations and reclaimed resources\n  - Safe-mode allows dry-run without actual deletion\n  - Audit logging for all cleanup operations\n  - Unit tests achieve >= 80% coverage\n  - Integration tests verify end-to-end GC flow\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - AR-005: Sandbox Creation Handler\n  - AR-006: Sandbox Deletion and Lifecycle Management\n  - AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: S\n  story_points: 3\n  days: 2\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-008/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775853550971,"end":1775853551377}}}}
